  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Our Discord Channel!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Join Ali Kemal on his fantastic journey on the path of true love!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1945780/extras/4391aab3d1c9664c1ca04a31e5bfd979.avif?t=1710161468\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>Under the Moon is an indie adventure - riddle game. If you're a riddle enthusiast you will have lots of fun while solving riddles in game while experiencing the stylized graphics, ambient soundtracks (which are exclusive for the level that you're in) and mellow atmosphere.<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br>More than 100+ riddles.<br>Playable 6 Map ( Turkey, China, Russia, Egypt, Germany, Scotland )<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1945780/extras/2c26f71230453125b42b401dfe3c55b6.avif?t=1710161468\" width=600 height=300 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Join Ali Kemal on his fantastic journey on the path of true love!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1945780/extras/4391aab3d1c9664c1ca04a31e5bfd979.avif?t=1710161468\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>Under the Moon is an indie adventure - riddle game. If you're a riddle enthusiast you will have lots of fun while solving riddles in game while experiencing the stylized graphics, ambient soundtracks (which are exclusive for the level that you're in) and mellow atmosphere.<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br>More than 100+ riddles.<br>Playable 6 Map ( Turkey, China, Russia, Egypt, Germany, Scotland )<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1945780/extras/2c26f71230453125b42b401dfe3c55b6.avif?t=1710161468\" width=600 height=300 /></span>",
